column5: Need 1 to 5 fishermen for a fly-in June 18th to 25th. trip is with Northern Outposts out of Armstrong, Ontario. This is to a brand new lake that has never had a cabin on it. Lake is about 180 miles north of Armstrong. Lake has walleyes and pike If interested e-mail [email protected] for further info Larry
What will the costs be for this trip? Has anyone fished the lake before?
